---

<BaseLayout
  title="HVAC Contractor in Phoenix, AZ | AC, Heating, Heat Pumps | Skyhooked on Comfort"
  description="Trusted HVAC technicians serving the Phoenix Valley since 2010. AC repair, heating, heat pumps, mini-splits, IAQ. 24/7 emergency. Licensed & insured. Call (480) 123-4567."
>

  <!-- ==========================================
       Section 1: Hero
       ========================================== -->
  <!-- Background: CSS gradient. TODO: add hero bg image via `style="background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg')"` with overlay -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center bg-navy-dark overflow-hidden"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(0.18 0.085 258) 0%, oklch(0.27 0.085 258) 50%, oklch(0.40 0.08 258) 100%);"
  >
    <!-- Decorative background shapes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full opacity-10" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.83 0.175 84), transparent);"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-20 w-80 h-80 rounded-full opacity-5" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.83 0.175 84), transparent);"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 lg:py-32 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sunshine/20 text-sunshine text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 font-body">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-sunshine opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-sunshine"></span>
        </span>
        24/7 Emergency Service Available Now
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
        Phoenix Valley's Most Trusted<br class="hidden sm:block"/>
        <span class="text-sunshine">HVAC Team.</span>
        <br class="hidden sm:block"/>Comfort, Done Right.
      </h1>

      <p class="font-body text-navy-50 text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        From a dead AC in 110° August heat to a brand-new heat pump install, Skyhooked on Comfort has kept the Phoenix Valley comfortable since 2010. EPA-certified technicians, upfront flat-rate pricing, and a 100% satisfaction guarantee on every job.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a
          href="tel:4801234567"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-sunshine hover:bg-sunshine-dark text-navy font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          Call (480) 123-4567
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-navy font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors"
        >
          Request a Quote →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust badges strip -->
      <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-navy-50 text-sm font-body" role="list">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
            Licensed & Insured
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 5.25a3 3 0 013 3m3 0a6 6 0 01-7.029 5.912c-.563-.097-1.159.026-1.563.43L10.5 17.25H8.25v2.25H6v2.25H2.25v-2.818c0-.597.237-1.17.659-1.591l6.499-6.499c.404-.404.527-1 .43-1.563A6 6 0 1121.75 8.25z"/></svg>
            AZ ROC-312489
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5"/></svg>
            EPA 608 Certified
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"/></svg>
            4.9★ Google (500+ reviews)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/></svg>
            Family Owned Since 2010
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ==========================================
       Section 2: Trust Strip
       ========================================== -->
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-neutral-100 py-8" aria-label="Trust signals">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-10" role="list">
        {[
          { icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/>`, label: 'Licensed & Insured' },
          { icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>`, label: 'Upfront Pricing' },
          { icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"/>`, label: '100% Satisfaction Guarantee' },
          { icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"/>`, label: 'Google 5-Star Rated' },
          { icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/>`, label: 'Family Owned Since 2010' },
        ].map(badge => (
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-navy font-body font-semibold text-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sunshine flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true" set:html={badge.icon}></svg>
            {badge.label}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ==========================================
       Section 3: Audience Selector
       ========================================== -->
  <section class="bg-navy-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-center mb-12">
        What can we help you with today?
      </h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Residential card -->
        <div class="group bg-white border-2 border-navy rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sunshine" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-2xl mb-3">For Your Home</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            From emergency AC repair on the hottest Phoenix day to full heat pump installs with federal tax credits — our residential team handles it all. Upfront pricing, same-day dispatch, and a 100% satisfaction guarantee on every visit.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/residential"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-navy hover:bg-navy-light text-white font-display font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            See Residential Services →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Commercial card -->
        <div class="group bg-white border-2 border-navy rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sunshine" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
